                      Employment
   General Information

   The City of Flagstaff Human Resources office is located on the first
   floor of City Hall, at 211 W. Aspen Ave. Hours are 8:00 a.m. to 5:00
   p.m. (winter) and 7:00 a.m. to 4:00 p.m. (summer), Monday through
   Friday.

   If you need a printed application, you may:
     * Stop by the Human Resources office located in City Hall at 211 West
       Aspen Avenue,
     * Call our job line at (520) 779-7698,
     * Download the application, click here.

   Applications may be mailed to out of town residents upon request. If
   you obtain a printed application instead of using our online
   application system, please be sure to include the Vacancy Number that
   is listed with the job opening. Applications will be accepted for
   current openings only. Resumes are accepted only with an application.
   Your application cannot be considered without the vacancy number.
   Applications must be received on or prior to the closing date to be
   considered.

   City Hall · 211 W. Aspen · Flagstaff, Arizona 86001 · (928) 774-5281
